                    ],
                    "text_description" : "주어진 식의 좌변을 간단히 하면 \\[ \\begin{array}{l} 3 x^{2}-\\left\\{x-2 x^{2}-(\\square-4 x)\\right\\}+6 \\\\ =3 x^{2}-\\left(x-2 x^{2}-\\square+4 x\\right)+6 \\\\ =3 x^{2}-\\left(-2 x^{2}-\\square+5 x\\right)+6 \\\\ =3 x^{2}+2 x^{2}+\\square \\square-5 x+6 \\\\ =\\square \\end{array} \\] 따라서 $\\square+5 x^{2}-5 x+6=5 x^{2}+x+9$ 이므로 \\[ \\begin{aligned} \\square & =5 x^{2}+x+9-\\left(5 x^{2}-5 x+6\\right) \\\\ & =5 x^{2}+x+9-5 x^{2}+5 x-6 \\\\ & =6 x+3 \\end{aligned} \\]"
